	(342, '_transient_owp_feed_data_a7b8e2d958ce6ae4458b12157bc8733d', '<ul><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'https://oceanwp.org/discover-how-easy-it-is-to-create-a-high-converting-landing-page-in-wordpress/?utm_source=wp-news-widget&utm_medium=wp-dash&utm_campaign=news-feed\' target=\'_blank\'>Discover How Easy It Is to Create a High Converting Landing Page in WordPress</a><div class="rssSummary">When you launch a new website, one of your biggest priorities is to attract visitors. This is not an easy task though. It takes a lot of hard work and&hellip;</div></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'https://oceanwp.org/comparing-free-and-paid-wordpress-hosting/?utm_source=wp-news-widget&utm_medium=wp-dash&utm_campaign=news-feed\' target=\'_blank\'>Comparing Free and Paid WordPress Hosting</a><div class="rssSummary">It wouldn’t be wrong to say that WordPress is one of the greatest content management systems in the world that can help you establish a strong web presence. With WordPress,&hellip;</div></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'https://oceanwp.org/how-to-monetize-your-wordpress-website/?utm_source=wp-news-widget&utm_medium=wp-dash&utm_campaign=news-feed\' target=\'_blank\'>How to Monetize Your WordPress Website</a><div class="rssSummary">Whether you want to bring your business online or start a blog to share your ideas, it has never been easier to create a website than today. Content management systems,&hellip;</div></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'https://oceanwp.org/partnering-with-cloudways/?utm_source=wp-news-widget&utm_medium=wp-dash&utm_campaign=news-feed\' target=\'_blank\'>Partnering with Cloudways – An Optimized Managed Cloud Hosting Platform for WordPress</a><div class="rssSummary">OceanWP takes great pride in announcing the partnership with Cloudways – Managed Cloud Hosting Platform – that has power-packed features and optimized stack for WordPress-based websites. We have worked together&hellip;</div></li></ul>', 'no'),
