ugin repository!</p>\n<p>This plugin <strong>integrates with and extends Autoptimize</strong>. It integrates with <a href="https://criticalcss.com/?aff=1">criticalcss.com</a>, a premium service which uses a &#8220;headless&#8221; browser to extract real critical CSS. That way it  fully automates the extraction of <strong>high-quality critical CSS</strong> and the creation of rules for that critical CSS. It can work <strong>100% automated</strong>, but also allows semi-automated jobs (where you enter a URL for which you want a specific rule, the power-up will do the rest) and manual rules (where you create the rule and add critical CSS yourself).</p>\n<p><a href="http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ao_critcss_saas.png"><img class="alignleft size-large wp-image-10630" src="http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ao_critcss_saas-1024x576.png" alt="" width="625" height="352" srcset="http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ao_critcss_saas-1024x576.png 1024w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ao_critcss_saas-300x169.png 300w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ao_critcss_saas-624x351.png 624w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ao_critcss_saas.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 625px) 100vw, 625px" /></a></p>\n<div class=\'yarpp-related-rss\'>\n<p>Possibly related twitterless twaddle:<ul>\n<li><a href="https://blog.futtta.be/2016/09/02/almost-time-to-announce/" rel="bookmark" title="Almost time to announce">Almost time to announce </a></li>\n<li><a href="https://blog.futtta.be/2018/03/04/want-to-test-automated-critical-css-creation/" rel="bookmark" title="Want to test automated Critical CSS creation?">Want to test automated Critical CSS creation? </a></li>\n<li><a href="https://blog.futtta.be/2012/12/20/2012-ffwd-high-performance-twenty-twelve-child-theme/" rel="bookmark" title="2012.FFWD; high performance Twenty Twelve child theme">2012.FFWD; high performance Twenty Twelve child theme </a></li>\n</ul></